msgctxt "#30354"
msgid "Install or activate the Doku-Kanal skin from addon settings."
msgstr "The Doku-Kanal skin is the look (theme) for Kodi that matches this addon.[CR][CR][B]Install[/B]: If the skin is not installed yet, find an entry under Settings → Skin to install it. The Doku-Kanal repository must be installed first (one-time ZIP install from the Releases page).[CR][CR][B]Activate[/B]: If the skin is already installed, go to Kodi Settings → Appearance → Skin and switch to \"Doku-Kanal (Skin)\".[CR][CR][B]Skin start-up[/B]: In addon settings you can enable \"Skin start-up on Kodi start\" – then skin background and settings are loaded when Kodi starts.[CR][CR][B]Where?[/B] Settings → Skin; Kodi Settings → Appearance."

